videos.headline: Wisconsin returns opening kickoff 91 yards to the house
videos.description: Wisconsin's Stephan Bracey takes the opening kickoff 91 yards to the house.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wisconsin returns opening kickoff 91 yards to the house) 2020/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nebraska's Markese Stepp muscles his way into the end zone
videos.description: Markese Stepp plows across the goal line for a Cornhuskers touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Markese Stepp crosses goal-line for 1-yard Rushing touchdown) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Braelon Allen finds pay dirt on impressive 71-yard run
videos.description: Braelon Allen breaks through the Cornhuskers' defense for a 71-yard Wisconsin rushing touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Braelon Allen runs for 71-yard Rushing TD) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Samori Toure hauls in the quick slant pass for a Nebraska TD
videos.description: Adrian Martinez hits Samori Toure with a slant for a Cornhuskers' touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Samori Toure makes catch for 4-yard Receiving touchdown) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wisconsin comes up big with INT
videos.description: Wisconsin Saftey Collin Wilder steps up to intercept Adrian Martinez's pass and give the Badgers momentum coming out of halftime.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Picked! Nebraska throws INT in the 3rd quarter) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wisconsin capitalizes off of INT with 17-yard TD
videos.description: Kendric Pryor hauls in a dart from Graham Mertz for a 17-yard touchdown, extending the Badgers lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Touchdown! Kendric Pryor scores vs. Nebraska) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Braelon Allen fights his way past the goal line for a Badgers TD
videos.description: Braelon Allen will not be denied as he pushes his way into the end zone to give Wisconsin the lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Braelon Allen rushes in for 3-yard Rushing touchdown) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Collin Wilder snags his 2nd INT of the game
videos.description: Wisconsin safety Collin Wilder shows his ball-hawk skills as he grabs his second interception off of Adrian Martinez.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Collin Wilder makes timely pick vs. Nebraska) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Marvin Scott III bursts through the middle for a Nebraska TD
videos.description: Marvin Scott III powers through the Badgers' defense to tie the game at 28.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Marvin Scott III crosses goal-line for 3-yard Rushing touchdown) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Braelon Allen breaks off 53-yard TD for his 3rd TD
videos.description: Braelon Allen turns on the jets and finds the end zone for his third touchdown of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Braelon Allen runs for 53-yard Rushing touchdown) 2021/11/20 ESHEET
